            <h3>How do I enable multi-factor authentication (MFA) on a WireGuard VPN?</h3>
            <p>With Defguard, MFA is enabled at the VPN gateway level through the admin panel. Unlike other solutions that only provide MFA for initial setup, Defguard implements true connection-level MFA that triggers every time a user attempts to connect to a protected VPN location.</p>
