            <h3>How does MFA improve the security of WireGuard VPN connections?</h3>
            <p>MFA adds critical security layers beyond WireGuard's cryptographic keys. Even if private keys are compromised, attackers cannot establish VPN connections without additional authentication factors. This prevents credential theft, insider threats, and unauthorized access to private networks.</p>
